highlights.text: “Without You” by 高爾宣 OSN has been on Top Songs Taiwan the longest, at 2345 days straight.
Jay Chou has the most spots on Top Songs Taiwan. “擱淺” is the highest at #36.
“多遠都要在一起” by G.E.M. is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Taiwan, up 76 spots at #118.
“The Dead Dance” by Lady Gaga is the highest new entry on Top Songs Taiwan at #171.
